  "remarks": "TAi.139 Title: Haji. Designation: Third Secretary, Taliban Consulate General, Karachi. Afghan passport no. D 000763 issued 9 Jan 1997. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Safi tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 29 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended 25 July 2006, 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011)",
